Ah, this issue appears intermittently even after cookies and cache are reset. I can't reproduce now. Can anyone help with this? 

I designed a manual to expand widths, but these element widths are variable inline styles dynamically set by the site at initialization runtime.

```adblock
photopea.com#$#.mainblock > .body { width: 100vw !important; }
photopea.com#$#.mainblock > .body > .strongset { width: initial !important; }
photopea.com#$#.mainblock > .body > .strongset > div [style*="width:"] { width: initial !important; }
photopea.com#$#.cmanager { width: initial !important; }
```
